e Rinero]]|FRA}} [[File:Jersey polkadot.svg|20px|link=Mountains classification in the Tour de France|alt=A white jersey with red polka dots.]] || {{ct|COF|1998}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 200\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2\n|{{flagathlete|[[Marco Pantani]]|ITA}} [[File:Jersey yellow.svg|20px|link=General classification in the Tour de France|alt=A yellow jersey.]] || {{ct|UNO|1998}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 175\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 3\n|{{flagathlete|[[Alberto Elli]]|ITA}} || {{ct|ALM|1998}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 165\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 4\n|{{flagathlete|[[C\u00e9dric Vasseur]]|FRA}} || {{ct|C.A|1998a}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 156\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 5\n|{{flagathlete|[[St\u00e9phane Heulot]]|FRA}} || {{ct|FDJ|1998}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 152\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 6\n|{{flagathlete|[[Jan Ullrich]]|GER}} || {{ct|TEL|1998}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 126\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 7\n|{{flagathlete|[[Bobby Julich]]|USA}} || {{ct|COF|1998}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 98\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 8\n|{{flagathlete|[[Michael Boogerd]]|NED}} || {{ct|RAB|1998}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 92\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 9\n|{{flagathlete|[[Leonardo Piepoli]]|SUI}} || {{ct|SAE|1998}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 90\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 10\n|{{flagathlete|[[Roland Meier]]|SUI}} || {{ct|COF|1998}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 89\n|}\n{{columns-end}}\n{{columns-start}}\n\n===Young rider classification===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Final young rider classification (1\u201310)<ref>{{cite web|title=Stage 21: Melun \u2013 Paris-Champs-\u00c9lys\u00e9es (147,5 km): Overall youth|url=http://www.letour.com/98us/etapes/21/classements/ijg.html|website=[[Tour de France]]|publisher=[[Amaury Sport Organisation]]|accessdate=10 September 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20000307185840/http://www.letour.com/98us/etapes/21/classements/ijg.html|archivedate=7 March 2000}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Rank!! scope=\"col\" | 