=== Uniform changes ===\n* In March 2019, the Rams announced they would debut new uniforms for the 2020 season.  The new logos and colors were revealed on March 23.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ramsnewlook.com/|title=Los Angeles Rams New Look|website=ramsnewlook.com|access-date=2020-03-23}}</ref>The new logos were heavily criticized.<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/25/sports/football/rams-logo-angelo-state.html</ref> The new uniforms will be revealed sometime in May.\n\n==Roster changes==\n\n=== Free agency ===\n\n==== Unrestricted ====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Los Angeles Rams|year=2020|border=2}}\" |Position\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Los Angeles Rams|year=2020|border=2}}\" |Player\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Los Angeles Rams|year=2020|border=2}}\" |2020 team\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Los Angeles Rams|year=2020|border=2}}\" |Date signed\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Los Angeles Rams|year=2020|border=2}}\" |Contract\n|-\n|-style=\"background:#cfc\"\n|[[Defensive end|DE]]\n|[[Michael Brockers]]\n|[[Los Angeles Rams]]\n| March 27\n|\n|-style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|[[Linebacker|ILB]]\n|[[Cory Littleton]]\n|[[Las Vegas Raiders]]\n|\n|\n|-style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|[[Linebacker|OLB]]\n| [[Dante Fowler]]\n| [[Atlanta Falcons]]\n|\n|\n|-style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|[[Wide receiver|WR]]\n| [[Mike Thomas (wide receiver, born 1994)|Mike Thomas]]\n| [[Cincinnati Bengals]]\n| \n|\n|-style=\"background:#cfc\"\n|[[Center (gridiron football)|C]]\n|[[Austin Blythe]]\n|[[Los Angeles Rams]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Quarterback|QB]]\n|[[Blake Bortles]]\n|\n|\n|\n|-style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|[[Placekicker|K]]\n|[[Greg Zuerlein (American football)|Greg Zuerlein]]\n|[[Dallas Cowboys]]\n|\n|\n|-style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|[[Cornerback|CB]]\n|[[Nickell Robey-Coleman]]\n|[[Philadelphia Eagles]]\n|\n|\n|-style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|[[Free Safety|FS]]\n|[[Marqui Christian]]\n|[[New York Jets]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Linebacker|LB]]\n|[[Bryce Hager]]